{"display":"Using the provided MOC_Intake_Form as a template, create a webpage that can accept form submisions. The webpage must include the example input, and the user must be able to provide their own answers. Use TypeScript or JavaScript (at your discretion) for field validation. At this time, all fields are required. Form submissions must be written to a single table in an SQLite database. Create two directories in the current working directory, \"webpage\" and \"data\". The directory named \"webpage\" will contain the HTML, scrpting, CSS, and other assets presented to the form submitter. The directory named \"data\" will contain only the SQLite database. Show me a list of the filesystem changes you want to make before proceeding.","pastedContents":{},"timestamp":1773151830155,"project":"/home/rstahl/src/repos/rhr-project-intake","sessionId":"7e205cfa-d4f7-45b6-9557-892d401da53f"}
